{"tid":2334432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英勉員工：《蘋果》一定做落去","createTime":"2020-12-21T07:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T07:42:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26b0fcf9fe51fd4cd6269cdcffd88b68e4f7187b","tid":2334432,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/HJL6DLE3N5DK3IDYCEEUK6CZFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FHJL6DLE3N5DK3IDYCEEUK6CZFE%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=a8615d9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FHJL6DLE3N5DK3IDYCEEUK6CZFE%2F&h=db749509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/HJL6DLE3N5DK3IDYCEEUK6CZFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n黎智英勉員工：《蘋果》一定做落去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vZgm4kb4SC6JmI_hSP7fsp3Htgk=/964x557/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SCRLPJ6GNRFEBFUXL3WOX4OAXM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvZgm4kb4SC6JmI_hSP7fsp3Htgk%3D%2F964x557%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSCRLPJ6GNRFEBFUXL3WOX4OAXM.gif&h=fc2d2a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英被關押在高設防的赤柱監獄。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被控欺..............定可以做落去」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台學者轟北京廢立會「港陷戒嚴時代」 籲台擔當關鍵角色施援<br />\n<br />\n黎智英上周五由荔枝角收押所轉到赤柱監獄關押後，首晚即遇上入冬以來最低溫，前日朝早市區氣溫僅12.5℃。至昨早市區最低氣溫更跌至11.9℃，再創入冬新低。昨早約8時半，張劍虹獨自到赤柱監獄探望黎，約9時45分離開。張步出監獄時稍稍展露歡顏，形容在獄中的黎十分精神，「佢好精神呀，話啲伙食OK，比想像中OK，冇（外間）講得咁差」，又指黎被關押期間平日主要「睇吓書」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹探望 斥當重犯看待<br />\n<br />\n張劍虹不忘轉達黎勉勵《蘋果》同事的心意：「佢叫同事唔使擔心，話除非係政治打壓就無得講，如果唔係《蘋果》一定可以做落去。」對於黎早前被懲教人員鎖上手銬及鐵鏈，押解往法庭提堂，又被調往高設防的赤柱監獄還柙，猶如重犯般看待，張坦言：「難過啦見到佢（黎）咁樣。」直斥當局「不嬲都係當重犯咁對待佢啦」，反問：「佢𠵱家係啲咩重犯啫！」<br />\n<br />\n縱然如此，談到高院排期本月23日開庭處理黎的保釋申請，張劍虹引述黎有信心可獲保釋，「佢有信心嘅，我哋盡力啦，盡力啦！」<br />\n<br />\n黎智英因被指違反工業邨用地租賃條款，本月3日被控欺詐解上法庭，還柙候訊；其後再被警方國安處引用港版國安法，起訴他勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全罪，解往西九龍裁判法院提堂，惟法庭下令要他還柙至明年4月16日再訊，被質疑是未審先囚。事件惹國際關注，前港督彭定康日前在網上撰文，將黎智英封為其心目中的年度人物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k7VQlrKgtVo7SpRLQJGRuTa1B2o=/1518x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DGIQHHZZORBKFMQKMJLR3QQDGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk7VQlrKgtVo7SpRLQJGRuTa1B2o%3D%2F1518x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDGIQHHZZORBKFMQKMJLR3QQDGA.jpg&h=f169c78f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《蘋果》社長張劍虹指黎在獄中十分精神。"},{"pid":"d59d82c336adfd5e623efad9c544ee23095392d3","tid":2334432,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"算係咁"},{"pid":"a55a5faee77ffb9e4399bb6cbdce4efc1dc7fa2b","tid":2334432,"uid":48026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:37:31.000Z","msg":"依家咪政治打壓囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a07be1a63e5aa77e41e496f2f51b2f66017730","tid":2334432,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"f0906152eacda96bcb08ac7bbfe0dbaf36d4d406","tid":2334432,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:41:27.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"010f51c90fce823567df436a79fdf9e4e875f213","tid":2334432,"uid":337289,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}